 ======================================
 Dependencies for running MTP navigator
 ======================================

   * python (>= 2.4)
   * python-gtk2 (>= 2.12)
   * python-glade3
   * pymtp (0.0.4 Pythonic binding to LibMTP to interact with MTP devices: http://nick125.com/projects/pymtp)
 
 Additional dependencies for getting tags from audio files:
 
   * python-eyed3 (for getting MP3 tags)
   * vorbis-tools (for getting OGG tags)
   
 =============================
 Install from a release tarbar
 =============================
  tar xzvf MTPnavigator-x.x.x.tar.gz
  cd MTPnavigator-x.x.x
  python setup.py install (as root)
 
 launch with command "mtpnavigator"
 
  =================================================
  Additional dependencies for building from sources
  =================================================
     
     * libgtk2.0-dev
     * make
 
  ==================================                     
  Install from subversion repository
  ==================================
  svn checkout svn://svn.berlios.de/mtpnav/trunk mtpnavigator
  cd mtpnavigator
 
  launch with command "make test"